ActCorrections and Conditional Release Act
PrecisDesignation of DENIS COUILLARD of Laval, Quebec, to be Vice-Chairperson of the National Parole Board, Quebec Regional Division for a period of five years, effective March 9, 2009; and reappointment of DENIS COUILLARD as a full-time member of the National Parole Board, Quebec Regional Division, to hold office during good behaviour, effective February 19, 2012 for a term ending March 8, 2014.
